<Base title="Camps" lang="en" description="Hungarian summer camps in Vancouver – the Diaspora School Camps.">
  <div class="container container--narrow prose">
    <h1 class="page-title">Camps</h1>

    <p>
      Hungarian camps have a long tradition in Vancouver. For decades we ran camps
      together with the other Hungarian school. We often welcomed guest presenters
      from Hungary, who held craft workshops and traditional Hungarian children's
      games. Folk dance, rhymes, and songs are essential parts of the daily
      activities.
    </p>

    <ul>
      <li><a href="/en/camps/2019"><strong>Diaspora School Camp 2019</strong></a></li>
      <li><a href="/en/camps/2022"><strong>Diaspora School Camp 2022</strong></a></li>
    </ul>

